{"published time": "2024-11-19T07:14:58+08:00", "images": ["https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/feat-apec-protest.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest1-1024x683.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest2.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest3.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest4.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest5.webp", "https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest6.webp"], "content": "<div class=\"post-thumbnail\">\n <img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"250\" sizes=\"(max-width: 562px) 100vw, 562px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/feat-apec-protest.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/feat-apec-protest.webp\" width=\"562\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"entry-content\">\n <div id=\"fb-root\">\n </div>\n <p>\n  <em>\n   Featured image: Yankee imperialism flag burnt during the protests against the APEC in Lima. Source: social media.\n  </em>\n </p>\n <p>\n  Between 15\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  and 16\n  <sup>\n   th\n  </sup>\n  of November, the APEC (Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation Forum) Summit took place in Lima, Peru. As Nuevo Per\u00fa\n  <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/11/08/nuevo-peru-yankees-go-home-updated/\">\n   denounced\n  </a>\n  , this attracted a new contingent of Yankee troops. The Peruvian people has called to protest against this summit and has made coincide this event with the national strike. We have\n  <a href=\"https://redherald.org/2024/11/16/international-news-briefing-strikes-in-peru-and-housing-struggles-in-france-and-spanish-state/\">\n   recently reported on the national strike and the recent protests\n  </a>\n  in the country. The old Peruvian State had prepared a contingent\n  <a href=\"https://www.infobae.com/peru/2024/11/13/dina-boluarte-lidera-cumbre-apec-2024-con-extremas-medidas-de-seguridad-ante-protestas-en-lima-contra-la-criminalidad/\">\n   of 33,000 national police officer\n  </a>\n  s deployed in Lima.\n </p>\n <p>\n  This big repressive deployment has not prevented the protests to take place the previous days and during the APEC Summit itself. Massive protests have taken place in the capital of Peru, where great combativeness by the protesters who have clashed with police have been witnessed. During the protests Yankee imperialism\u2019s flags were burned, the imperialist intervention in Peru has been protested and has been shouted: \u201cYankees out of Peru!\u201d:\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   https://twitter.com/Caterin49788702/status/1857091861371863238\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  The repressive forces have been even cornered and forced to retreat in several occasions due to the strength of the protests:\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   https://twitter.com/AlertaNews24/status/1857515265078014214\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  There are numerous images and videos of clashes and combative protests:\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-embed\">\n  <div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n   https://twitter.com/SeNoticiasPlus/status/1857116502501020120\n  </div>\n </figure>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n  <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19171\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"683\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest1-1024x683.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest1-1024x683.webp\" width=\"1024\"/>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Source: AP Foto/Silvia Izquierdo\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-1 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19172\" data-id=\"19172\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"300\" sizes=\"(max-width: 681px) 100vw, 681px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest2.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest2.webp\" width=\"681\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19173\" data-id=\"19173\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"348\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 560px) 100vw, 560px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest3.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest3.webp\" width=\"560\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19174\" data-id=\"19174\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"575\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1023px) 100vw, 1023px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest4.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest4.webp\" width=\"1023\"/>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Source: Adriana N\u00fa\u00f1ez Rabascall, Voz de Am\u00e9rica\n </p>\n <figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\">\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19175\" data-id=\"19175\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"312\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest5.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest5.webp\" width=\"500\"/>\n  </figure>\n  <figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\">\n   <img alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-19176\" data-id=\"19176\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" src=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest6.webp\" srcset=\"https://redherald.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/apec-protest6.webp\" width=\"960\"/>\n  </figure>\n </figure>\n <p>\n  Source: Diario Sin Fronteras\n </p>\n <p>\n  Nine protesters\n  <a href=\"https://larepublica.pe/politica/2024/11/18/al-menos-nueve-detenidos-solo-en-lima-por-protestas-durante-foro-apec-1080072\">\n   have been detained\n  </a>\n  so far.\n </p>\n</div>", "pdf_content": "", "pdf_links": [], "source": "https://redherald.org/2024/11/18/yankees-out-of-peru-cry-in-lima-against-the-apec/", "type": "article", "title": "\u201cYankees out of Peru!\u201d cry in Lima against the APEC \u2013 The Red Herald", "description": "Between 15th and 16th of November, the APEC (Asia-Pacific Economic Cooperation Forum) Summit took place in Lima, Peru.", "modified time": "2024-11-18T23:15:05+00:00", "author": ["A.R."], "categories": ["Featured", "The Americas"], "tags": ["Peru"], "sections": ["Featured", "The Americas", "Peru", "English", "pll_673bca735d290"], "source_name": "Red Herald"}